{"ts": "2026-06-09T16:34:34.804406+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:K8QOce | successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14cdb62b2e100f4ebf75f88cf5c58669437208e3)", "id": "lc_b09fb886-eb8b-48e7-8360-0ade294a2754"}, {"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:K8QOce | # vue3-vite-starter-template\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | A single page app [Vite](https://vitejs.dev) starter template, created to easily bootstrap Vue.js 3 apps.\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | **Features**\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | - Vitest for unit testing\n| MCP:K8QOce | - Pinia for state management\n| MCP:K8QOce | - Vue Router 4 for client-side routing\n| MCP:K8QOce | - Bootstrap 5.3 for layout and styling\n| MCP:K8QOce | - SCSS variables inside Vue components\n| MCP:K8QOce | - Purgecss for eliminating unused CSS\n| MCP:K8QOce | - Basic multiple layouts feature\n| MCP:K8QOce | - ESLint config based on `eslint:recommended` with sensible defaults :relaxed:\n| MCP:K8QOce | - [Prettier](https://prettier.io/) for code formatting\n| MCP:K8QOce | - Automated release workflow with [semantic-release](https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release)\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ## Project setup\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | pnpm install\n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ### Compiles and hot-reloads for development\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | pnpm run dev\n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ### Compiles and minifies for production\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | pnpm run build\n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ## Run your unit tests\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | pnpm run test:unit\n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ### Lints files\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | pnpm run lint\n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ### Lints and fixes files\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | npm run lint-fix\n| MCP:K8QOce | ```\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | ### Customize configuration\n| MCP:K8QOce | \n| MCP:K8QOce | See [Configuration Reference](https://vitejs.dev/guide/).", "id": "lc_85b33f11-200c-415a-a21f-a0a088ab7ec2"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "9617c264-dde2-4d99-b524-1ca3305593fc", "tool_call_id": "call_91409ed74b4740849f056cdc", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
