{"ts": "2026-06-09T16:35:14.773301+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## Answer: Contributors are expected to use **pnpm**; npm is **not acceptable**.\n\nThere are three independent pieces of evidence in the repository that all point the same direction:\n\n### 1. `package.json` — Active enforcement via `preinstall` script\n```json\n\"preinstall\": \"npx only-allow pnpm\",\n```\nThis is a lifecycle hook that runs **before** any `npm install` or `yarn install` completes. The [`only-allow`](https://github.com/nicolo-ribaudo/only-allow) package checks which package manager invoked the script and **hard-errors** if it isn't `pnpm`. This means running `npm install` or `yarn install` will intentionally fail.\n\n### 2. `package.json` — Corepack `packageManager` field\n```json\n\"packageManager\": \"pnpm@10.20.0\",\n```\nThis is the [Node.js Corepack](https://nodejs.org/api/corepack.html) declaration. When Corepack is enabled (it ships with Node 16.9+), it will automatically intercept any `npm` or `yarn` command and redirect to `pnpm@10.20.0`, further locking in pnpm as the required tool.\n\n### 3. `README.md` — Documentation instructions\nAll \"Project setup\" commands use pnpm:\n```\npnpm install\npnpm run dev\npnpm run build\npnpm run test:unit\npnpm run lint\n```\n(The one stray `npm run lint-fix` line in the README appears to be a typo/inconsistency, since every other command is `pnpm`.)\n\n### 4. Lock file\nThe repository contains only a **`pnpm-lock.yaml`** — there is no `package-lock.json` (npm) or `yarn.lock`. This is consistent with pnpm being the sole supported manager.\n\n### Conclusion\nThe project **actively enforces pnpm** at install time (via the `only-allow` preinstall guard) and **declares it formally** (via the `packageManager` Corepack field). Using `npm install` will fail. Contributors **must** use pnpm.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 766, "prompt_tokens": 6747, "total_tokens": 7513, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 298, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 5376}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "mimo-v2.5-pro", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "cb7b1a9a1f0549d48291dca482c1ae6f", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ead3c-9130-7173-813f-4c92f524567b-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 6747, "output_tokens": 766, "total_tokens": 7513, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 5376}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 298}}}}]}}}
